                     <note>Brot úr Rannsóknaþætti og Ómagabálki.</note>
                     <!--<bibl><ref target="Gragas1852">Grágás Ib, Kbh. 1852</ref>, bls. 231-34</bibl>
<bibl><ref target="Gragas1883">Grágás III, Kbh. 1883</ref>, bls. 490-501</bibl>
